/1 = "Correct"
/2 = "Incorrect"
/3 = "Ok, let's try this one instead"
</item>

**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************
	EDITABLE INSTRUCTIONS: change instructions here
**************************************************************************************************************
**************************************************************************************************************
<instruct>
</instruct>

<page intro1>
<h1>Anagram Task</h1><hr><br>
In this task you will be asked to solve <u>anagrams</u>.<br><br>
An anagram presents an arrangement of letters such as 'semou' that can be rearranged into an English word
such as 'mouse'.<br><br>
Your task will be to unscramble the anagram and find the hidden word.<br><br><br>
Continue on to learn more about the task.
</page>

<page intro2>
<h1>Anagram Task</h1><hr><br>
You will be asked to solve 10 anagrams and you will have have <%parameters.anagramTimeout/1000/60%> minutes
to solve each one. Each anagram has only one solution.<br><br>
You can submit as many solutions as you want during the <%parameters.anagramTimeout/1000/60%> minutes.<br><br>
If your solution is <b>incorrect</b>, you can try again.<br>
If your solution is <b>correct</b>, you will automatically move on to the next anagram.<br>
If you <b>run out of time</b>, you will automatically move on the next anagram.<br><br>
You can also skip any anagram by entering 'SKIP' into the textbox. The program will immediately present you with
the next anagram from the queue.<br><br><br>
Start with your first anagram when you are ready.
</page>


<text instruct>
/ items = ("Enter the solution and click 'Next' to continue.
You can enter the word 'SKIP' at any time and the next anagram will start automatically")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 3%, false, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 10%)
/ size = (90%, 20%)
/ vjustify = center
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
/ erase = false
</text>

<text finish>
/ items = ("Thank you!")
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 8%, true, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 50%)
/ size = (80%, 10%)
/ vjustify = center
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
</text>

<button exitbutton>
/ caption = "EXIT"
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 3%, false, false, false, false, 5, 1)
/ position = (50%, 80%)
/ size = (30%, 8%)
/ valign = center
/ halign = center
</button>

